      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically robust A80 Supra Turbo featuring the revered 2JZ-GTE power plant. This unit retains its sequential twin-turbocharger setup, ensuring linear power delivery across the RPM band. The drivetrain is anchored by the Getrag V160 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory Torsen limited-slip differential for optimal power transfer. Recent maintenance includes a comprehensive refresh of the cooling system and vacuum lines to ensure boost pressure remains within factory parameters. The suspension retains its original double-wishbone architecture, providing the precise kinematic response the JZA80 is known for. A driver-focused example",
