      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This vehicle is a fantastic example of a well-cared-for daily driver that remains in impressive condition. The exterior paint holds a deep, glossy shine, with only the minor, inevitable stone chips on the front bumper that come with standard road use. All body panels are straight, and the alloy wheels are free of major curb rash. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean and has never been smoked in. The leather upholstery is supple with only light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster, and all interior plastics and trim pieces are intact and scratch-free. Every electronic feature, including the premium surround-sound system, dual-zone climate control, and heated power seats, operates exactly as it should. Mechanically, the car is sound; it has been serviced at regular intervals, and the engine pulls strongly and smoothly. The transmission shifts are crisp, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping",
